# Merchant Original Bundle Reference Cache

This file intentionally keeps a compact project-owned reference so future work does not need to reopen the installed original game folder for routine parity planning.

Original bundle inspected:

- `D:\Games\merchant_of_the_six_kingdoms\resources\app.asar`
- Main renderer in bundle: `\dist\electron\renderer.js`
- Bundle style: Electron/Vue app with one large bundled renderer and static assets

